These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Music-Genre: ambient, metal, house, folk
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Music-Genre:metal##2
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:house is between Music-Genre:metal and Music-Genre:ambient##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | metal   | house | ambient       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Music-Genre: rock, d&b, techno, electronic
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Music-Genre:techno and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Music-Genre:electronic is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Music-Genre:rock is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | rock | techno | electronic |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

