2. Flower:orchid is between Flower:poppy and Food:corn##2
3. Flower:poppy is on the far left##1
4. Flower:dahlia is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Flower:dahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Flower   | poppy | orchid   | dahlia | begonia |

